author: Rebecca Davison For Mailonline
title: Beckham children wear £4300 clothes in one day | Daily Mail Online
text: A £1,800 handbag and £240 Gucci boots for Harper... as well as £550 Burberry trench coats for Romeo and Cruz... it's a good job brand Beckham is worth '£240million' The collective price for the children's outfits comes in at around £4300 Victoria's children Brooklyn, 17, Romeo, 14, Cruz, 11, and Harper, five, were all on the front row for support The British fashion designer, 42, was debuting the AW17 ready to wear collection from her eponymous label Ex-Spice Girl Victoria has shown her designs at New York Fashion Week - as opposed to London - since 2008 David, 41, a former professional footballer, has flown to the States to be with her amid his email scandal Last weekend, leaked email correspondence saw him brand the Honours Committee ‘unappreciative c***s’ after being passed over for a knighthood
